flowchart TD
    A[Loaded AssetRecord list] --> B[Group by section]
    B --> C[FilterSelectionDialog]
    C --> D{User checks filter only?}
    D -- yes --> E[Select all records in that filter]
    D -- no, double click --> F[LabelSelectionDialog]
    F --> G[User checks individual labels]
    G --> H[Store explicit selected records]
    E --> I[Selected records ready]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Generate preview labels]
